<h2 id="creating-new-tools">Creating new tools</h2>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">K</code>: delete a line.</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">U</code>: un-delete a line.</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">O</code>: save the file (â€˜Oâ€™ stands for â€˜outputâ€™). <em>You will also need to press Enter to confirm the filename!</em></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code> + <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">X</code>: exit the editor.</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>nano dates.sh
input <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="nb">cut</span> <span class="nt">-d</span> , <span class="nt">-f</span> 1 seasonal/<span class="k">*</span>.csv
bash dates.sh
</code></pre></div></div>

